# SaaS clone template — business memory

- **Parent business repo:** `Github/business-saas-clone-template` (`buildngrowsv/business-saas-clone-template`) with `children/<slug>/` per monetized SKU
- **Standalone child business repos:** `Github/business-saas-clone-template-children-*` when split for git remotes
- **Template:** `Github/business-operations/general-sops/BUSINESS-MEMORY-TREE-CURRENT-AND-TARGET-ARCHITECTURE.md` §1.2 and §8 (nested collections)

Child-only rules stay in each child **code** repo under `.cursor/rules/` when that repo is the workspace root.
